      • xGroupCreate

        public com.buession.lang.Status xGroupCreate(String key,
                                             String groupName,
                                             StreamEntryId id,
                                             boolean makeStream)
        从接口复制的说明: StreamCommands
        This command creates a new consumer group uniquely identified by groupname for the stream stored at key

        详情说明 https://redis.io/commands/xgroup-create/

        参数:
        key - Key
        groupName - Group Name
        id - ID
        makeStream - Can use the optional MKSTREAM subcommand as the last argument after the id to automatically create the stream (with length of 0)
